{
  "stem": "16503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was a guessing game.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I think the grownups felt it much more than I did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then we were called up-- a certain group.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It must have been end of December.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were taken to the famous railway track, put on-- into a railway car, which was a car like normal people go in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were-- it wasn't a long train, and we were squeezed in, but at least you were sitting on a bench.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't know where, and we went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Mother and my sister stayed together, and the rest we did not know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We did not know a soul.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we never encountered the people which we started from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we went on this train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I do not know how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It wasn't-- and we stopped in a small station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They got us out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now we are under the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They are waiting there for us, and obviously, that was a Wehrmacht who was unfit for the-- for the front-- old guys, cold, under-dressed, everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And we were taken-- it was about 200 of us approximately-- through a village, which was quite picturesque actually, if you want to go into-- into something.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And you could see that the people were looking through their nice little windows-- curtains-- looking at these horrible looking things which were coming through their village.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we finished at the end of the village in a barn, which was equipped with bunks and a huge latrine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the commandant of that-- it was a labor camp-- we were digging ditches in the forest in Kurzbach in Germany in-- it's a very forest-- geographically, full of forests.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we were housed in this barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We were under the Wehrmacht, which was watching us.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
